                            <comment id="13556508" author="jdcryans" created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 19:32:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch we eventually need to apply. We need to keep setting dfs.client.read.shortcircuit.skip.checksum so that a newer HBase running on an older HDFS would still work, although double checksumming may happen.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
